Metrics.Name: kestrel.active_connections
Metrics.Description: Number of connections that are currently active on the server.

Metrics.Name: kestrel.connection.duration
Metrics.Description: The duration of connections on the server.

Metrics.Name: kestrel.queued_connections
Metrics.Description: Number of connections that are currently queued and are waiting to start.

Metrics.Name: http.server.active_requests
Metrics.Description: Number of active HTTP server requests.

Metrics.Name: aspnetcore.routing.match_attempts
Metrics.Description: Number of requests that were attempted to be matched to an endpoint.

Metrics.Name: http.client.active_requests
Metrics.Description: Number of outbound HTTP requests that are currently active on the client.

Metrics.Name: http.client.request.duration
Metrics.Description: The duration of outbound HTTP requests.

Metrics.Name: http.client.open_connections
Metrics.Description: Number of outbound HTTP connections that are currently active or idle on the client.

Metrics.Name: http.client.connection.duration
Metrics.Description: The duration of successfully established outbound HTTP connections.

Metrics.Name: http.client.request.time_in_queue
Metrics.Description: The amount of time requests spent on a queue waiting for an available connection.

Metrics.Name: dns.lookup.duration
Metrics.Description: Measures the time taken to perform a DNS lookup.
